## 10. Code Examples

### Hello World (Adequate Version)

```torture
require ecc;
function public callable returnable void main()
    code size 2048 max stack size 256
    requires security level 1
    allowed roles admin
{
    proceed verifyfunctionidentity();
    authorize invocation of println
        at security level 1
        with memory limit 128
        with timeout 1000
        with io operation because literal "outputting greeting is I/O"
        with justification "hello"
        with arguments { value by value = literal "Hello, World!" }
        discarding return
        predictstackdepth 4
        with authority chain admin
        with approval of alwaysapprove
        with approval justification "greeting approved"
        with approval timeout 1000;
}
```

### Variable Declaration with Full Disclosure

```torture
declare mutable readable writable
    purpose computational
    scope local
    int:32 score = 92;
```

### Grade Classification (Enterprise Edition)

```torture
if (score authorize use operator >= 90 because literal "checking excellence threshold")
    judging authorized by root because literal "academic affairs authorizes excellence judgment"
    expects elseifs 1 else 1
{
    proceed authorize invocation of println
        at security level 1
        with memory limit 128
        with timeout 1000
        with io operation because literal "outputting grade requires I/O"
        with justification "excellent"
        with arguments { value by value = literal "Excellent" }
        discarding return predictstackdepth 4
        with authority chain admin
        with approval of alwaysapprove
        with approval justification "excellent output approved"
        with approval timeout 1000;
}
```

### Struct Declaration with Mandated Methods

```torture
struct record = struct {
    declare mutable readable writable purpose storage scope local int:32 amount;
} implement {
    method public callable returnable void init(...)  ...
    method public callable returnable void destroy()  ...
    method public callable returnable void copy()     ...
    method public callable returnable void move()     ...
    method public callable returnable void serialize() ...
    method public callable returnable void deserialize() ...
    method public callable returnable void tostring()   ...
    method public callable returnable void fromstring() ...
    method public callable returnable void hash()       ...
    method public callable returnable void compare()    ...
    method public callable returnable void equals()     ...
    method public callable returnable void getproperty() ...
    method public callable returnable void setproperty() ...
    method public callable returnable void invoke()     ...
    method public callable returnable void getsize()    ...
    method public callable returnable void alignof()    ...
    method public callable returnable void defaultvalue() ...
    method public callable returnable void validate()   ...
    method public callable returnable void mutate()     ...
    method public callable returnable void clone()      ...
}
```

Every struct **must implement all 19 methods**. This guarantees that every TortureLang data structure is fully lifecycle-managed.

